<a name="526">&nbsp;</a>
<h4>Turnkey Booth Upgrades</h4>
Simplify your planning and upgrade to a turnkey booth package for the 2013 CES!<br />
If you have an in-line booth (10X10, 10X20, 10X30), you are eligible for a turnkey upgrade. Our turnkey booth packages allow you to streamline costs and eliminate the hassle of ordering all the various components of your booth. Everything will be in place when you arrive, and you&rsquo;ll save yourself time and money.&nbsp;<br />
There are three turnkey options to choose from:<br />
<ul>
	<li>
		<strong>Turnkey A</strong> provides all of your basic exhibit needs such as a counter, table, chairs, shelves, electrical and&nbsp;company ID sign</li>
	<li>
		<strong>Turnkey B</strong> includes backlit graphics to illuminate your branding and attract potential customers</li>
	<li>
		<strong>Turnkey C</strong> includes all the great offerings of a turnkey package, plus basic Internet and a 46&rdquo; monitor</li>
</ul>
Upgrade today! All Turnkey pricing is inclusive of booth space, so you only need to pay for the difference is price.&nbsp;<br />
